::Killfest::

Killfest sends a private comm to DrillBit, stating that he had no 
idea what the old Predacon cave was or where it is, and asking for 
its location.




--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "Richard Allen" <rfa007@h...> wrote:
> ::DrillBit::
> 
> "Roger that, Killfest."
> He opened a commlink, on a codded channel.
> "Everyone pull out and meet at the old Predicon cave, now!"
> 
> ::Dollen::
> 
> He heard the coom chatter, and pulled himself out of the ruble.
> "Why is it always me?" He says to himself, heading towards the 
> meeting location.
